

To use fileCompressor, you must use the following command-line interface:

	./fileCompressor <flag: "-c" or "-d"> <.txt or .hcz file> <codebook>

		or

	./fileCompressor -R <flag: "-c" or "-d"> <directory> <codebook>
	
		or 

	./fileCompressor -R -b <directory> 

		or
	
	./fileCompressor -b <.txt file> 


